Gain experience in Human-Computer Interaction research, namely user-centered research skills, including user study design and data analysis;
Opportunity for top-tier academic publications (e.g., CHI, UIST); depending on the student’s commitment and contributions, they may co-author a research paper.

Desired Skills:
